---
title: South Indian Chicken Thigh Curry with Garlic Butter Rice & Tomato Salad
description: This slow-cooker curry boasts South Indian flavours, with curry powder and coconut milk intermingling with juicy chicken thigh. Time transforms these separate ingredients into a cohesive and delicious meal, served over fragrant garlic rice. It’s like a hug in a bowl!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66cfd2fa5e32858493913439-cdb730b7.jpeg
